Dhe kjo shnderrohet ne nje zhgenjim te plote ndaj jush,

00:31:17.600 --> 00:31:20.300
dhe harroni qe dliresia eshte kaq e rendesishme.

00:31:20.300 --> 00:31:23.300
Pra sa me lart te jete nje njeri ne jete,

00:31:23.600 --> 00:31:25.500
te zere pozicion me te larte,

00:31:25.800 --> 00:31:35.000
me e larte behet ajo qe e quani ego- merr perkedhelje,

00:31:35.300 --> 00:31:39.500
me shume e shtyn poshte ne Vishuddhin e majte.

00:31:39.900 --> 00:31:43.000
Pra nje person i tille arratiset ne Vishuddhin e majte,

00:31:43.300 --> 00:31:45.700
sepse thelle ne zemer,

00:31:45.700 --> 00:31:47.900
ne ndergjegjen e tij ai ndihet fajtor.

00:31:48.200 --> 00:31:51.900
Dhe e gjitha vazhdon si nje faj,

00:31:52.500 --> 00:31:54.300
faj ne Vishuddhin e majte.

00:31:54.700 --> 00:31:57.900
Dhe kur shkon si faj ne Vishuddhin e majte

00:31:58.300 --> 00:31:59.900
behet nje situate e veshtire,

00:32:00.100 --> 00:32:01.500
sepse nje person i tille,

00:32:01.900 --> 00:32:03.700
behet ekstremisht i ndjeshem.

00:32:03.900 --> 00:32:06.600
Nje gje ti thuash dhe ai do te ndihet fajtor.

00:32:07.100 --> 00:32:09.700
Ti perpiqesh te kurosh Vishuddhin e tij te majte,

00:32:09.700 --> 00:32:12.000
pastaj ai behet edhe me keq.

00:32:12.500 --> 00:32:15.400
Eshte nje situate shume e keqe me njerezit e Vishuddhit te majte,

00:32:15.700 --> 00:32:19.100
dhe ka njerez qe jane te Vishuddhit te majte te cilet

00:32:19.400 --> 00:32:20.800
japin gjithmone shpjegime.

00:32:21.900 --> 00:32:24.600
Nje person qe ka Vishuddhin e djathte do jete arrogant,

00:32:24.900 --> 00:32:28.100
njerezit e Vishuddhit te majte kane nje metode shume dinake

00:32:28.100 --> 00:32:32.300
te kthimit te pergjigjes dhe shpjegimeve per cdo gje.

00:32:32.300 --> 00:32:33.400
Cfaredo te thoni, ata do te thone,

00:32:33.400 --> 00:32:35.500
"Jo Nene, kjo eshte keshtu, kjo eshte keshtu."

00:32:35.500 --> 00:32:39.200
Kjo eshte nje gje. Jo vetem kjo, s'mbaron ketu,

00:32:39.500 --> 00:32:41.200
ju jep sarkazem.

00:32:41.900 --> 00:32:45.400
Kjo eshte arsyeja pse njerezit ne Perendim nuk flasin hapur,

00:32:45.400 --> 00:32:47.000
gjithmone jane sarkastike.

00:32:47.600 --> 00:32:50.200
Ata mendojne se eshte budallallek te flasesh hapur,

00:32:50.800 --> 00:32:51.900
s'eshte inteligjente,

00:32:52.200 --> 00:32:55.500
nese dhe derisa te flasesh ne menyre shume sarkastike

00:32:55.900 --> 00:32:58.800
qe e dini ndonjehere eshte shume e veshtire per tu arritur.

00:33:01.200 --> 00:33:04.200
Kjo eshte menyra e shtrember se si ata flasin.

00:33:04.700 --> 00:33:09.500
Dhe kjo pandershmeri vjen prej ketij problemi te Vishuddhit te majte.

00:33:09.500 --> 00:33:11.400
Nese Vishuddhi i majte eshte kaq keq,

00:33:11.700 --> 00:33:17.100
nuk mund te arrini asgje qe eshte e embel,

00:33:17.600 --> 00:33:19.000
qe eshte e bukur,

00:33:20.500 --> 00:33:22.200
qe eshte e vlefshme.

00:33:23.800 --> 00:33:26.800
Vishuddhi i majte nuk do te vleresoje kurre.

00:33:27.200 --> 00:33:28.800
Ata qe vuajne nga Vishuddhi i majte

00:33:28.800 --> 00:33:31.200
s'mund ta vleresojne kurre personin tjeter, s'munden kurre.

00:33:31.900 --> 00:33:34.200
Do te kete fjalen e vet, do te mendoje, "Une jam me i miri"

00:33:34.400 --> 00:33:36.500
sepse i duhet te ekzistoje,

00:33:37.000 --> 00:33:39.400
se problemi duhet te ekzistoje, pra si?

00:33:39.400 --> 00:33:42.300
Eshte nje lloj i egos se semure

00:33:42.700 --> 00:33:44.000
qe nuk do te pranoje

00:33:44.000 --> 00:33:45.600
qe dikush mund te jete me i mire se une,

00:33:45.600 --> 00:33:47.300
qe me duhet te ndjek dike,

00:33:47.600 --> 00:33:50.300
qe me duhet te mesoj nga dikush tjeter.

00:33:50.700 --> 00:33:51.900
Kam pasur shume shembuj;

00:33:51.900 --> 00:33:53.900
E shoh sidomos tek njerezit qe jane me Mua,

00:33:53.900 --> 00:33:57.200
Gjej se ata futen ne Vishuddhin e majte shume shpejt

00:33:57.900 --> 00:34:00.800
per shkak te mungeses se protokollit.

00:34:00.800 --> 00:34:02.800
Kur fillojne te kene mungese protokolli

00:34:02.800 --> 00:34:05.200
ata shkojne ne Vishuddhin e majte.

00:34:05.400 --> 00:34:07.800
Pra te jeni me Mua eshte bekim, pa dyshim,

00:34:08.000 --> 00:34:11.800
por gjithashtu duhet te jesh shume shume i kujdesshem

00:34:12.000 --> 00:34:14.600
qe te mos e kaloni protokollin.

00:34:14.900 --> 00:34:17.800
Mos u mundoni te hidheni me perpara,

00:34:18.400 --> 00:34:20.100
vetem te krekoseni.

00:34:20.700 --> 00:34:25.200
Disa njerez e kane zakon te kapercejne kufijte

00:34:25.200 --> 00:34:26.900
dhe sapo ju te kaloni kufijte

00:34:26.900 --> 00:34:28.900
krijohet Vishuddhi i majte.

00:34:29.400 --> 00:34:32.300
Nuk duhet te kete frike per Nenen tuaj,

00:34:32.500 --> 00:34:34.200
duhet te kete respekt per Nenen tuaj,

00:34:34.200 --> 00:34:38.000
gje qe ruhet nga Vishuddhi juaj i majte.

00:34:39.200 --> 00:34:43.400
Tani kjo eshte nje fuqi shume e fshehur e Shri Ganeshes.

00:34:43.700 --> 00:34:46.800
Ajo qe e quani se eshte fuqia e Ganeshes

00:34:46.800 --> 00:34:52.300
eshte Vishuddhi i majte duke vepruar si dliresia.

00:34:55.200 --> 00:35:01.700
Fuqite e Ganeshes jane shprehur te gjitha nepermjet Vishuddhit te majte.

00:35:03.500 --> 00:35:06.400
Pra ata qe besojne ne Ganesha, ne pafajsine e paster,

00:35:06.400 --> 00:35:09.200
duhet te dijne qe ne sjelljen tuaj te perditeshme,

00:35:09.500 --> 00:35:12.800
ne veprimet e perditeshme,

00:35:13.500 --> 00:35:15.000
duhet te kete dliresi.

00:35:15.300 --> 00:35:19.800
Ganesha eshte shfaqur si lulet e dliresise.

00:35:20.700 --> 00:35:24.500
Dhe vetem shihni, nese ne ligjin e hyjnores nuk ka dliresi,

00:35:24.500 --> 00:35:26.300
si i kufizoni (caktoni kufijte) njerezit,

00:35:26.300 --> 00:35:28.600
si i beni mire,

00:35:28.900 --> 00:35:30.800
si i pastroni ata,

00:35:31.100 --> 00:35:33.000
si i beni ata te evoluojne?

00:35:33.400 --> 00:35:37.800
Supozojme nje peme po rritet dhe nuk ka kufij ne te,

00:35:38.000 --> 00:35:40.400
ajo vetem rritet si nje gje e eger,

00:35:40.400 --> 00:35:41.800
nuk ka ku kufij,

00:35:41.800 --> 00:35:43.300
me pas cfare do dale nga ajo?

00:35:43.300 --> 00:35:44.500
Asgje.

00:35:44.800 --> 00:35:48.300
Pra per te bere nje person sa me te larte,

00:35:48.300 --> 00:35:50.000
duhet ta kufizoni ate (caktoni kufijte).

00:35:50.500 --> 00:35:53.100
Babai im jepte nje shembull te mire te kesaj,

00:35:53.100 --> 00:35:56.400
nese merr pak grure, fara gruri dhe
.

00:35:58.400 --> 00:36:00.400
Ne doni te dilni jashte dilni,

00:36:00.600 --> 00:36:04.200
por mos shqetesoni njerezit, duke levizur perreth.)

00:36:06.800 --> 00:36:08.700
Shikoni, edhe kjo eshte nje gje tjeter.

00:36:08.900 --> 00:36:11.700
Gjithe keto gjera s'jane asgje por

00:36:11.700 --> 00:36:14.000
turbullira te Vishuddhit te majte.

00:36:14.500 --> 00:36:19.500
Kuptoni, gjithe keto shqetesime te reklamuara

00:36:19.900 --> 00:36:22.500
ose perpjekje per mbizoterim,

00:36:23.000 --> 00:36:26.000
ose nje person shume i hedhur apo i fryre (mendjemadh)

00:36:26.000 --> 00:36:28.400
te gjitha keto vijne nga Vishuddhi i majte,

00:36:28.400 --> 00:36:30.800
sepse ju doni te kaperceni Vishuddhin tuaj te majte

00:36:30.800 --> 00:36:32.300
prandaj e beni.

00:36:33.300 --> 00:36:35.300
Me pas i shtohet edhe kjo.

00:36:35.600 --> 00:36:38.900
Sa me shume provoni ta kaperceni, aq me shume iu shtohet juve.

00:36:39.200 --> 00:36:42.500
Tani duhet t'ju tregoj historine e babait,

00:36:42.500 --> 00:36:44.000
ai tha qe nese

00:36:44.000 --> 00:36:48.100
keni grurin dhe e shperndani (hidhni pa kriter) ate,

00:36:44.887 --> 00:36:46.428
(Dikujt ne salle - Ju lutem mos me shqetesoni.

00:36:48.100 --> 00:36:50.600
ai vetem shkon kot sic ndodh me vemendjen.

00:36:52.000 --> 00:36:54.000
Por nese e vini ne nje torbe pelhure,

00:36:54.500 --> 00:36:55.500
ne nje cante,

00:36:56.000 --> 00:37:00.800
ju mund ta mblidhni grumbull (tog) dhe ai mund te arrije lartesi.

00:37:01.600 --> 00:37:02.800
Ne te njejten menyre,

00:37:03.000 --> 00:37:06.100
nese e shkon kot vemendjen tende pa dliresi,

00:37:06.300 --> 00:37:07.900
ajo shperndahet;

00:37:08.800 --> 00:37:11.800
nuk ka kufij, nuk ka forma,

00:37:11.800 --> 00:37:13.200
nuk ka trajte.

00:37:13.400 --> 00:37:14.800
Por nese ti e kufizon ate,

00:37:15.800 --> 00:37:20.000
atehere ju beheni me i larte me i larte me i larte,

00:37:20.300 --> 00:37:24.500
dhe mund te ngrihesh me lart ne jeten tende shpirterore.

00:37:25.000 --> 00:37:29.600
Meqe ju jeni njerez qe doni te keni nje jete shume shpirterore,

00:37:29.900 --> 00:37:36.800
duhet te kuptoni qe Vishuddhi i majte duhet te korrigjohet.

00:37:37.700 --> 00:37:41.700
Tani, si e korrigjoni Vishuddhin e majte?

00:37:42.600 --> 00:37:44.800
Ndonjehere lodhem shume me ta,

00:37:44.800 --> 00:37:47.000
ndihem vertet- lodhem shume,

00:37:47.300 --> 00:37:49.300
Thjesht heq dore prej tyre.

00:37:49.900 --> 00:37:51.800
Sepse nese ato po ju kapin (ngercet).

00:37:51.800 --> 00:37:53.200
dhe ju u thoni " Po me kapni"

00:37:53.500 --> 00:37:55.900
ato behen edhe me keq. C'rreth vicioz qe eshte.

00:37:56.300 --> 00:37:57.800
Cila eshte kura per kete?

00:37:57.800 --> 00:38:01.900
Si ta thyejme kete rreth vicioz?- duke e perballur ate.

00:38:02.800 --> 00:38:05.000
Duhet te themi, "Cfare, po ndihesh fajtor per cfare?

00:38:05.000 --> 00:38:06.900
Po beni te njejtin gabim perseri e perseri,

00:38:06.900 --> 00:38:08.600
dhe ende jeni duke e bere."

00:38:08.600 --> 00:38:14.300
Duhet ti beni te gjitha injeksionet vetes.

00:38:14.500 --> 00:38:17.600
Por ne vend te kesaj fillojne te Me thone,

00:38:17.900 --> 00:38:20.900
"Jo, Nene. Jo, Nene. Jo, Nene."

00:38:21.400 --> 00:38:24.100
I thoni vetes, "Jo, une vete."

00:38:25.100 --> 00:38:28.000
Sot kam bere kete, neser do te bej kete,

00:38:28.000 --> 00:38:29.400
te pasnesermen do te bej kete.

00:38:29.400 --> 00:38:33.700
Ndal tani, ndal." Dhe ndalo ne kete pike.

00:38:34.300 --> 00:38:37.700
Atje ju ushtroni fuqine e Vishnumaya.

00:38:38.200 --> 00:38:41.800
Fuqia e Vishnumaya duhet te neutralizohet,

00:38:43.000 --> 00:38:46.500
nese eshte keshtu, prej gabimeve tuaja;

00:38:46.900 --> 00:38:51.900
por nese do ti duhet tju ktheje ne fuqite e saj

00:38:52.200 --> 00:38:53.900
ju duhet te perdorni fuqite e Vishnumaya

00:38:53.900 --> 00:38:56.300
duke i dhene vetes goditje.

00:38:59.400 --> 00:39:01.000
Vetem ju mund ta beni kete.

00:39:01.000 --> 00:39:03.800
Pra ne kete pike, ne piken e Vishnumaya

00:39:03.800 --> 00:39:05.900
Une vertet deshtoj ndaj jush.

00:39:06.300 --> 00:39:08.100
Ju duhet ta beni kete.

00:39:10.200 --> 00:39:13.500
Dhe prandaj une po mendoja per kete puja

00:39:13.800 --> 00:39:17.300
qe kur ju njerez te benit kete puja ndaj Meje,

00:39:17.900 --> 00:39:22.200
nese them ndonje gje do te krijoj me shume Vishnumaya tek ju.

00:39:22.200 --> 00:39:24.900
Por kjo eshte gjeja me e lehte te menaxhosh gjerat, me kuptoni -

00:39:24.900 --> 00:39:29.100
"Po ndihem fajtor" - jeni te mbaruar.

00:39:29.500 --> 00:39:31.900
"E mora ndeshkimin, e quajta veten fajtor."

00:39:32.300 --> 00:39:36.200
Eshte si ne gjyq juria ju thote qe jeni fajtor

00:39:36.200 --> 00:39:39.600
- mire, e pranoj, "Une jam fajtor," por jo ndeshkimin,

00:39:40.900 --> 00:39:42.200
pa marre ndeshkim.

00:39:42.700 --> 00:39:45.500
Nese ke vepruar gabim, atehere ndeshkoje veten.

00:39:45.800 --> 00:39:47.500
Ka dy menyra per te ndeshkuar njerezit.

00:39:47.900 --> 00:39:50.700
Njera eshte qe disa  ndeshkohen

00:39:50.700 --> 00:39:53.600
duke thene qe "Nuk do te kem ushqim."

00:39:53.600 --> 00:39:56.700
Por ata njerez qe kane zakonin e te mos pasurit ushqim

00:39:56.700 --> 00:39:59.300
e keto gjera, mund edhe te behen agresive

00:39:59.300 --> 00:40:01.300
me kete lloj zakoni te trazojne te tjeret

00:40:01.300 --> 00:40:05.700
per te mos ngrene ushqim. Them, qeniet njerezore jane shume te pasinqerta.

00:40:06.200 --> 00:40:07.700
Dijne si ta vrasin veten

00:40:07.700 --> 00:40:09.400
me nje thike tinzare gjithe kohes.

00:40:09.800 --> 00:40:12.000
Pra nuk ka menyre si ta korrigjosh veten.

00:40:13.100 --> 00:40:15.300
Nese te duhet te korrigjosh veten,

00:40:15.700 --> 00:40:19.200
atehere duhet ta perballesh veten ne menyren e duhur.

00:40:20.700 --> 00:40:23.100
Te supozojme keni bere dicka gabim,

00:40:23.700 --> 00:40:26.800
atehere duhet te beni dicka qe

00:40:26.800 --> 00:40:29.100
do ju pelqeje ta beni normalisht,

00:40:30.500 --> 00:40:31.700
dhe te ndeshkoni veten.

00:40:31.700 --> 00:40:33.500
Ju duhet, ju duhet, me vjen keq,

00:40:33.500 --> 00:40:35.500
ju nuk duhet te beni dicka

00:40:35.500 --> 00:40:37.200
qe normalisht do ju pelqente ta benit.

00:40:37.200 --> 00:40:39.200
Ashtu si te korrigjosh veten;

00:40:39.200 --> 00:40:45.600
te themi qe dikush eshte shume i dhene ndaj lulishteve, luleve.

00:40:46.200 --> 00:40:47.500
Kur beni gabime

00:40:47.500 --> 00:40:50.300
per pak kohe nuk shihni lule,

00:40:52.300 --> 00:40:54.700
vetem mbyllni syte tuaj per lule.

00:40:55.200 --> 00:40:58.000
Ka njerez, te supozojme,

00:40:58.200 --> 00:41:02.300
qe jane te dhene pas te kenduarit,

00:41:04.200 --> 00:41:08.300
keshtu nese beni gabime direkt ndalojne se kenduarit.

00:41:12.900 --> 00:41:14.900
Keshtu ju duhet te godisni.

00:41:15.800 --> 00:41:19.000
Duhet ta dini qe Vishnumaya eshte nje rrufe,

00:41:19.300 --> 00:41:21.300
dhe leksioni duhet te jete i tille.

00:41:21.700 --> 00:41:24.900
Nuk mund te jete aq i bute, sic ishte Shri Krishna.

00:41:25.300 --> 00:41:27.700
Po ju them qe eshte nje gje shume e fuqishme,

00:41:28.000 --> 00:41:34.800
dhe mundte Zoti te zgjoje ate fuqi te brendshme te Vishnumaya

00:41:35.100 --> 00:41:39.100
Eshte gjeja me e fuqishme qe nje qenie njerezore mund te kete,

00:41:39.400 --> 00:41:41.000
eshte gjeja me fatlume;

00:41:41.000 --> 00:41:43.800
ju beheni nje personalitet i shenjte.

00:41:46.600 --> 00:41:50.400
Kjo eshte nje nga menyrat e gjetjes se realizimit te Zotit.

00:41:51.400 --> 00:41:54.500
Kjo ishte nje pyetje e bukur e pyetur me vend,

00:41:54.800 --> 00:41:56.300
tamam ne kohe dje,

00:41:56.600 --> 00:41:59.500
te stabilizoni dliresine tuaj

00:42:00.200 --> 00:42:01.800
- por jo duke dhene bandhan,

00:42:01.800 --> 00:42:04.800
duke marre vibrime nga Nena dhe me pas t'i humbisni,

00:42:05.000 --> 00:42:07.900
jo ne kete menyre: ju vete te korrigjoni veten

00:42:08.100 --> 00:42:09.800
nga mengjesi ne darke,

00:42:10.800 --> 00:42:13.900
dhe te perballni veten pa u ndjere fajtore,

00:42:15.500 --> 00:42:17.500
dhe te mesoni gjera te reja.

00:42:18.100 --> 00:42:21.500
